 <p>
  <em>
   Mario + Rabbids Sparks of Hope
  </em>
  was one of the best-selling retail games in Japan at the time of its launch, but Ubisoft claimed at the start of 2023 that the title underperformed in terms of sales. The sequel has managed to mount a comeback, with
  <em>
